query:
UPDATE photos
                    SET title = $2,
                        filename = $3,
                        location_taken = $4,
                        date_taken = $5
                    WHERE 
                        id = $1
                    RETURNING 
                        id as "id!",
                        title as "title!",
                        filename as "filename!",
                        location_taken as "location_taken!",
                        date_taken as "date_taken!",
                        created_at as "created_at!",
                        updated_at as "updated_at!",
                        $6 as "cloudflare_resource!"
